      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Dealeth falsely, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Heb. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "doing falsehood",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; as if that were their whole work, the proper and peculiar sin of the priests and prophets, to deceive the people, and to flatter them by false visions, as in the next verse; not that they were not also guilty of the other sins, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Isaiah 56:11",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
