            "text": "Jeremiah 5:31",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", for they were all involved in the same wickedness; but the prophet mentions those sins that were most peculiar to each party. See the same ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
