  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "For from the least of them even unto the greatest of them,.... From the least in age to the oldest among them; or rather, from persons of the lowest class of life, and in the meanest circumstances, to those that are in the highest places of trust and honour, and are in the greatest affluence of riches and wealth; so that as men of every age and station had sinned, old and young, high and low, rich and poor, it was but just and right that they should all share in the common calamity: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "everyone is given to covetousness; which is mentioned particularly, and instead of other sins, it being the root of evil, and was the prevailing sin among them: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "from the prophet even unto the priest everyone dealeth falsely; the false prophet, as Kimchi interprets it, and so the Septuagint and other versions; and the priest of Baal, as the same interpreter; both acted deceitfully; the one in prophesying lies to the people, the other in drawing them off from the pure worship of God. The Targum is, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "\"from the scribe to the priest;'' ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "from the lowest order of teachers to the highest in ecclesiastical office. The whole shows a most general and dreadful corruption. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "from the lowest order of teachers to the highest in ecclesiastical office. The whole shows a most general and dreadful corruption. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
